00:00:10.840 --> 00:00:12.920
When I realized I had to get a divorce,

00:00:12.921 --> 00:00:15.881
I had a neighbor that the two of us were having kids at about, like.

00:00:15.882 --> 00:00:17.801
We had some kids that kind of lined up in age.

00:00:17.802 --> 00:00:19.441
We had pregnancies similar.

00:00:19.442 --> 00:00:22.561
We would share. It was like the cutest shit that you would want.

00:00:22.562 --> 00:00:24.361
And our husbands were kind of similar.

00:00:24.362 --> 00:00:25.761
And I didn't really like her husband,

00:00:25.762 --> 00:00:28.621
but I had every excuse in the world for my husband.

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:30.840
I was different. Our relationship was different.

00:00:30.841 --> 00:00:33.021
Our. She didn't understand our shit.

