00:00:39.322 --> 00:00:41.121
like it was winter or whatever.

00:00:41.122 --> 00:00:42.481
And then she said to me, hey,

00:00:42.482 --> 00:00:44.201
you know, can we start doing those morning walks again?

00:00:44.202 --> 00:00:45.361
Cause I really need a friend.

00:00:45.362 --> 00:00:46.161
I need to talk to somebody.

00:00:46.162 --> 00:00:46.681
And I was like, yeah,

00:00:46.682 --> 00:00:49.001
for sure. And all we could do was, like,

00:00:49.002 --> 00:00:50.241
walk two blocks and come back.

00:00:50.242 --> 00:00:52.021
We both had to get back to our kids.

00:00:52.240 --> 00:00:54.120
