00:00:54.121 --> 00:00:55.801
of arguments that she was having with her husband.

00:00:55.802 --> 00:00:57.241
And I would be like, wow.

00:00:57.242 --> 00:00:59.081
And I would be giving her all this advice, like, girl,

00:00:59.082 --> 00:01:00.601
you deserve better. That's not okay.

00:01:00.602 --> 00:01:01.841
