00:01:11.120 --> 00:01:12.840
I'm gonna give somebody else this advice.

00:01:12.841 --> 00:01:15.521
Like, I can see how wrong it is in somebody else's marriage,

00:01:15.522 --> 00:01:18.561
but I'm making every fucking excuse in the book for my marriage.

00:01:18.562 --> 00:01:21.041
And thank god I had a friend coming to me,

00:01:21.042 --> 00:01:23.201
and I was able to have that internal insight

00:01:23.202 --> 00:01:26.541
to realize I'm lying to my goddamn self.

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:29.280
I'm the reason I'm being treated this way,

00:01:29.281 --> 00:01:30.821
because I'm fucking staying.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:33.440
I can leave and I can figure some shit out.

00:01:33.441 --> 00:01:35.181
There's no reason I have to stay.

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:37.380
And that's when I fucking woke up and left.

00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:40.520
I realized, because you could tell yourself whatever little fancy story,

00:01:40.521 --> 00:01:41.521
but at the end of the day,

00:01:41.522 --> 00:01:42.861
I thought, what if he died?

00:01:43.120 --> 00:01:45.440
What if you were dead and literally not here?

00:01:45.441 --> 00:01:48.521
What would I do then? And from that point on,

00:01:48.522 --> 00:01:51.941
I started making moves, and I changed my own life.

